        """Run the enhanced bot with user management, fixed quote editing, and Dynamics 365"""
        logger.info("ðŸš€ Starting Enhanced Multi-Ceiling Bot v8.7 with USER MANAGEMENT & DYNAMICS 365...")
        logger.info("âœ¨ COMPLETE USER PROFILES + ONBOARDING + AI MEMORY + ADMIN MANAGEMENT + FIXED QUOTE EDITING + DYNAMICS 365!")
